OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSpells of rain in the northwest
OL,6,Fedging slowly southeast with showers
OL,7,Ffollowing. Low cloud and coastal mist
OL,8,Fin the west and southwest. Drier
OL,9,Felsewhere with sunny spells. Very warm
OL,10,For hot in the southeast and feeling
OL,11,Fmuggy.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FRain continues southeast and
OL,14,Feases overnight. Clear spells and
OL,15,Fisolated showers into the northwest,
OL,16,Fwhere a little fresher. Warm and muggy
OL,17,Fin the south and southeast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
