OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FRather cloudy at first with
OL,6,Fa little light rain in the south.
OL,7,FIsolated showers in the north.
OL,8,FGenerally dry with sunny spells
OL,9,Fdeveloping for most. Feeling a little
OL,10,Fless warm.
